7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both ContentStudio and Copy.ai share a solid foundation of core features including Short Form, Templates, Tone Control, Multilingual. Where ContentStudio pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Browser Extension, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. On the other hand, Copy.ai uniquely offers Long Form, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, ContentStudio holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Copy.ai scores 7/10 overall and 9/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Copy.ai comes in at a lower starting price of Free, while ContentStudio begins at $25/mo. Copy.ai stands out by offering a free plan, giving you a risk-free way to explore the platform. ContentStudio requires a paid subscription from the start."}]]}]
